high_descs: turn around and walk over to the front of the kitchen stove
grab the fork off of the kitchen counter to the left of the stove
turn around and bring the fork over to the kitchen sink
place the fork inside of a cup inside the sink
pick the cup up from the kitchen sink
turn around and move forwards to the kitchen island counter
place the cup on top of the kitchen island counter
anns.task_desc: place a cup with a fork in it on top of the kitchen island counter

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the left side of the stove.
Take the fork off the counter.
turn around and walk to the sink on the right.
Put the fork in the goblet that's in the sink.
Pick up the goblet.
Turn around.
Put the goblet on the table to the left of the fork.
anns.task_desc: Put a goblet with a fork in it on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the island in the center of the kitchen, then hang a right and walk up to the left side of the stove.
Pick up the metal fork that is on the kitchen counter to the left of the stove.
Turn around and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Place the metal fork handle down into the glass that is in the sink.
Pick up the glass with the metal fork in it.
Turn around and walk over to the kitchen island.
Place the glass with the metal fork in it onto the top of the kitchen island to the left of the closest metal fork.
anns.task_desc: Place a glass with a fork in it onto the kitchen island.
